title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 § 263.3 - Partnerships
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 § 263.3 - Partnerships

State Regulations

Tax Law, § 14(b) of § 1340(c), § 1342; Codes and Ordinances
of the City of Yonkers, §§ 92-111(b), 92-113

In general, every partnership doing business in the City of

Yonkers and having any partners who are nonresidents of the City of Yonkers
must file a City of Yonkers partnership return. For more information with
respect to the requirement to file a City of Yonkers partnership return, see
section
267.9
of this Title. Notes
